Zimplats Talks With Zimbabwean Authorities Continue After Plan Is Rejected

-- B y   V i c t o r i a   B a t c h e l o r
-- 
2011-08-23T00:15:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-23/zimplats-talks-with-zimbabwean-authorities-continue-after-plan-is-rejected.html
Zimplats Holdings Ltd. (ZIM)  said the
Zimbabwe Minister of Indigenisation and Economic Empowerment
rejected its Indigenisation Plan and directed that a revised
plan which complies with the legislation be resubmitted within
14 days. Talks between management and the relevant authorities
in this regard are ongoing, the company said in a regulatory
filing.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Victoria Batchelor at 
 vbatchelor@bloomberg.net  